# sync_media_to_s3.ignore — skip these paths for sync and upload.
# Matched against the file path relative to each source root (e.g. C:\Movies\).
#
# Glob syntax: * (any chars) and ? (one char). Use forward slashes.
#   **/pattern  — match in any subfolder
#
# Regex: prefix with re: (Python regex; also used for watcher/cp)
#
# VAM capture folders — skip timestamp-prefixed work-in-progress (YYYYMMDD-HHMMSS)
